<英文法規名稱>Standards Governing Calculation of Years of Teaching and Scope of Teaching Major Legal Courses for Arbitrator Waived from Training Requirement</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>仲裁人免經訓練任教年資計算及講授主要法律科目範圍標準</中文法規名稱>
